\id GAL Galatians in Boko, Ross Jones 2/08
\h Galatiↄ
\toc1 Galatiↄ
\toc2 Galatiↄ
\toc3 Gal
\mt1 GALATIƆ
\imt1 Yã́ pↄ́ kú láɛ bee guuↄ
\ip Galati bùsu gbɛ̃eↄ Yesu baona mà wa sì Pↄlu wɛ̃́lɛgɛa gɛ̃n plaade ń a àaↄ̃deo guuɛ (Zĩn 16.6, 18.23). Ãma waasokɛn pãleↄ gɛ̀ we lↄ, ↄ̃ aa dàda gbɛ̃́ↄnɛ aa mɛ̀, sema Yesude pↄ́ aa dɛ Yudaↄ ũↄ misiilɛ Mↄizi ikoyãɛ, aai tↄ̃zↄ̃. Pↄlu kĩ́i yãdanɛ bee bↄ̀ Yesu Kilisi yã́ kpɛɛ, àlɛ Galati bùsu Yesudeↄ da zↄbleu. Kɛ́ a mà gbɛ̃́piↄ lɛ́ swã́sɛ yã́pizi, ↄ̃ à láɛ bee kɛ̃̀nɛ́.
\ip Kɛ́ Pↄlu ye a gbɛ̃́ↄ ɛa laaidↄ baona zɛ́ mɛ̀ndonawa, ↄ̃ à yãdàdanɛ́ à mɛ̀:
\imq À azĩa yã́ bↄↄlɛkɛ̀nɛ́, aà nↄ̀sɛlilɛa ń lɛdoũ pↄ́ wa kɛ̀ ń kↄ̃o ń Yelusalɛũ dↄaanaↄ ikoyãpi musu ń a kↄ̃yãmasai ń Piɛɛo yã́pi musuo. Pↄlu a zĩnakɛyã bↄↄlɛkɛ̀nɛ́, à kpàlɛ à sìwà kɛ́ a zĩnakɛpi bↄ̀ Dii kĩ́iɛ (1-2).
\imq À gbãa'è Luabaakuańnↄ káau yã́ↄwa, ↄ̃ à mɛ̀ gbɛ̃e a e bↄ maa Mↄizi ikoyã maà sabaio, sema Yesu Kilisi náaikɛa (3-4).
\imq À tɛkpàńgu aa wɛtã wàↄ ńzĩa vĩ ń Lua Nisĩna dↄaaanɛ́o, asa Nisĩnapi ì yãmaaↄ inɛ́ dasi, a sɛ̃́ia mɛ́ yeakↄ̃zi ũ (5-6).
\ip À kũ̀ Yesu gãli píi ń Yesudeↄ píi swã́sɛ Pↄlu yã́pizi, aai sí ń nↄ̀sɛmɛndoo kɛ́ aa e bↄ zↄblea bui píiu.
\c 1
\s1 Baona pãle kuo
\p 
\v 1-2 Ma Lua zĩna Pↄlu ń ma Yesude dee pↄ́ wá sãnuↄ píi wámɛ wa láɛ bee kɛ̃̀ Yesude pↄ́ aa ku Galati bùsuuↄnɛ.\f + \fr 1.1-2 \ft Zĩn 16.6\f* Ma zĩnakɛ i bↄ gbɛ̃nazĩna kĩ́io, gbɛ̃nazĩna mɛ́ i a lɛdↄɛkɛo, Yesu Kilisi ń Mae Lua pↄ́ aà bↄ̀ gauo mɛ́ ma zĩ.
\v 3 Lua wá Mae ń Dii Yesu Kilisio gbɛ̃kɛkɛɛ́, aai á gba aafia.
\v 4 Kilisipi gì a wɛ̃nii Lua wá Mae pↄeãwa, à wá duuna kɛ̃̀wá, kɛ́ à e wá bↄ dṹnia tia vãiɛ beeu.
\v 5 Lua mɛ́ gawi vĩ gↄↄpii! Ãmi.
\p 
\v 6 Kɛ́ álɛ bↄ Lua pↄ́ á sisi a gbɛ̃kɛ guu kpɛ màa gↄ̃̀ↄ, álɛ zɛ ń bao koleao, yã́pi dìa maamaaɛ.
\v 7 Baona pãle kuo. Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ye Kilisi baopi lilɛↄ lɛ́ á liaaɛ.
\v 8 Baa tó wápiↄ ge malaikae bↄ̀ luabɛ à baona pↄ́ i kpaaĩ ń pↄ́ pↄ́ wá òɛ́oo waasokpàɛ́, Lua láaikɛwà.
\v 9 Wá òɛ́ yãa mɛ́ málɛ oɛ́ lↄ, tó gbɛ̃e baona pↄ́ i kpaaĩ ń pↄ́ pↄ́ á màoo waasokpàɛ́, Lua láaikɛwà.
\p 
\v 10 Málɛ sáau wɛɛlɛ gbɛ̃nazĩnawa yã̀, ge Luaɛ? Málɛ wɛɛlɛ ma yã́ ká gbɛ̃nazĩnagu yã̀? Tó gbɛ̃nazĩna má ye à káńgu e tia, dↄ̃ Kilisi zↄ̀blenan ma ũo.
\s1 Yesu Pↄlu sɛa a zĩna ũ
\p 
\v 11 Ma gbɛ̃́ↄ, má ye à dↄ̃ kɛ́ baona pↄ́ mi kpáɛ́ i bↄ gbɛ̃nazĩna kĩ́io.
\v 12 Mi ma gbɛ̃nazĩna kĩ́io, gbɛ̃e mɛ́ i damɛɛo, Yesu Kilisi mɛ́ bↄ̀ mↄ̀oa.
\p 
\v 13 Á mà lá má kú yãa Yudaↄ zɛ́u. Ma Yesudeↄ wɛtã̀ wɛ̃́lɛ ń wɛ̃́lɛo pãsĩpãsĩ, má wɛ̀ɛlɛ mà ń midɛ.\f + \fr 1.13 \ft Zĩn 8.3\f*
\v 14 Ma Yudaↄ zɛ́pi yã́ kũ̀ ↄplapla dɛ ma sáaↄla dasi, ma ãia dɛńla wá deziↄ fɛlɛkaayãpi guu.
\v 15 Ãma Lua ma dilɛ a pↄ́ ũ za ma da nↄ̀sɛu.\f + \fr 1.15 \ft Isa 49.1\f* Kɛ́ aà ma sísia a gbɛ̃kɛ guu gↄↄ kàɛ̀,
\v 16 ↄ̃ à a Nɛ́ gbàɛa,\f + \fr 1.16 \ft Zĩn 9.3-6\f* kɛ́ mà aà baona kpá buipãleↄnɛ. Mi gɛ́ kpálɛi gbɛ̃e gɛ̃zĩo,
\v 17 mi gɛ́ Yelusalɛũ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa dɛ zĩnaↄ ũ ma ãaↄ kĩ́io, ma gɛ Laalubuↄ bùsuu gↄ̃̀ↄɛ, ↄ̃ ma ɛa ta Damasi.
\p 
\v 18 Wɛ̃̀ àaↄ̃ gbɛa ↄ̃ ma gɛ Yelusalɛũ, kɛ́ wà kↄ̃ dↄ̃ ń Piɛɛo, ↄ̃ ma kɛaànↄ gↄↄ gɛ̃o.\f + \fr 1.18 \ft Zĩn 9.26-30\f*
\v 19 Mi zĩna pãle eo, sema Dii dãuna Zaaki bàasio.
\v 20 Yã́ pↄ́ má kɛ̃̀ɛ́pi, má sì ń Luao, ɛɛ málɛ tóo.
\v 21 Bee gbɛa ma gɛ Sili bùsuu ń Silisi bùsuo.
\v 22 Gↄↄ bee Yesude pↄ́ kú Yudeↄ i wɛsimalɛo,
\v 23 ãma aa su mà wà mɛ̀, gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ lɛ́ ń wɛtã yãa mɛ́ lɛ́ zɛ́ pↄ́ á wɛ̀ɛlɛ kaalɛpi waasokpa tiasa,
\v 24 ↄ̃ aa Lua tↄbↄ̀ ma yã́ musu.
\c 2
\s1 Pↄlu kↄ̃ yãmaa ń zĩna pãleↄ
\p 
\v 1 Wɛ̃̀ gɛ̃o mɛ̀ndosai gbɛa ma ɛa gɛ Yelusalɛũ ń Baanabao.\f + \fr 2.1 \ft Zĩn 15.2-4\f* Ma Titu sɛ̀, à gɛ̀wanↄ lↄ.
\v 2 Ma gɛ we, kɛ́ Lua mɛ́ bↄ̀ mↄ̀oa à kũ̀ mà gɛɛ. Ɔ̃ ma baona pↄ́ mi kpa buipãleↄnɛ bↄↄlɛkɛ̀ dↄaanaↄnɛ ńtɛ̃ɛ, kɛ́ zĩ pↄ́ má kɛ̀ ń pↄ́ pↄ́ málɛ kɛo su kɛ pão.
\v 3 Titu pↄ́ wá sãnu ń a Gɛlɛkikɛo, aai gãnawà aà tↄ̃zↄ̃o.
\v 4 Yesude ɛgɛna pↄ́ gɛ̃̀ wá guu kpã́iↄ mɛ́ aa yã́pi dà. Aa gɛ̃̀ wá naa Kilisi Yesuwa wɛ̃́ɛkɛa tàasikaiɛ. Aa ye wá da zↄbleuɛ,
\v 5 ↄ̃ wi we wa misìilɛnɛ́o baa yↄↄ, kɛ́ à e àↄ baona sĩana kũa yã́i.
\v 6 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ wàlɛ ń gwa dↄaana ũↄ, aai yãe kã́fĩmɛɛo. Lá aa dɛ, i kɛmɛɛ yãe ũo, asa Lua lí gbɛ̃e zãboo.
\v 7 Aa è Lua a baonakpaa buipãleↄnɛ nàmɛɛ ma ↄzĩ, lá à a kpaa Yudaↄnɛ nà Piɛɛɛ a ↄzĩwa.
\v 8 Asa lá Lua zĩkɛ̀ Piɛɛ guu a zĩnakɛ yã́ musu Yudaↄ kĩ́i, màa à zĩkɛ̀ ma guu buipãleↄ kĩ́i.
\v 9 Zaaki ń Piɛɛo ń Zãa pↄ́ wàlɛ ń gwa Lua kpɛ́ gbapɛlɛ ũↄ gbɛ̃kɛ pↄ́ Lua kɛ̀mɛɛ dↄ̃̀, ↄ̃ aa ↄkpàwá, wá ń Baanabao gbɛ̃kɛ vĩa ń kↄ̃o seela ũ. Aa sì wápiↄ wà gɛ́ buipãleↄ kĩ́i, ḿpiↄ sↄ̃ Yudaↄ kĩ́i.
\v 10 Yã́ pↄ́ aa yei lé, ń taasideↄ yã́ àↄ dↄwágu. Gↄↄ bee sↄ̃ wá mɛ wã̀ ń a kɛao kↄ̀.
\s1 Yesu náaikɛa mɛ́ ì wá suaba
\p 
\v 11 Kɛ́ Piɛɛ mↄ̀ Antiↄsi, ma giɛ̀ wɛliwɛ kɛ́ à zã̀ yã́wa yã́i.
\v 12 Asa e Zaaki zĩnaↄ aaↄ gɛ́ kái, ì pↄble ń buipãleↄɛ. Kɛ́ aa kà, ↄ̃ à bↄ̀zã à kɛ̃̀má, kɛ́ àlɛ vĩakɛ Yuda pↄ́ aa zɛ̀ ń tↄ̃zↄ̃yãoↄnɛ yã́i.
\v 13 Yuda kĩniↄ nàwà mↄafilipi guu. Baa se aa Baanaba gà nàmá.
\v 14 Kɛ́ má è aa baona sĩana kũa a zɛ́wao, má ò Piɛɛɛ ampii wáa: N Yuda ia ń kú lán buipãlewa, i kɛ lán Yudawa no. Kpelewa ńyↄ̃ fↄ̃ gãna buipãleↄwa aaↄ Yudaↄ yã́ kũai?
\p 
\v 15 Yudaↄn wá ũ, buipãle pↄ́ aa Lua dↄ̃oↄn wá ũo.
\v 16 Ãma wá dↄ̃ kɛ́ gbɛ̃e lí bↄ maa zĩkɛa ikoyãpiwa yã́io, sema Yesu Kilisi náaikɛa ado bàasio.\f + \fr 2.16 \ft Lom 3.20, 22\f* Baa wápiↄ, wa Kilisi Yesu náaikɛ̀, kɛ́ wà e bↄ maa wá Kilisi náaikɛapi yã́iɛ, i kɛ zĩkɛa ikoyãpiwa yã́i no, asa gbɛ̃e lí bↄ maa zĩkɛa ikoyãwa yã́io.\f + \fr 2.16 \ft Soũ 143.2\f*
\v 17 Gↄↄ pↄ́ wálɛ wɛɛlɛ wà bↄ maa naa Kilisiwa, tó wá è duunkɛnaↄn wá ũ sↄ̃, bee mɛ̀ Kilisi lɛ́ duuna wɛ̃zĩgba yã̀? Aawo!
\v 18 Tó ma ɛa lɛ́ ikoyã pↄ́ má gbòo kɛkɛ, a tàaeden ma ũ we.
\v 19 Asa má dɛ gɛ ũ ikoyãpi musuɛ, ↄ̃ ma bↄ a yã́u kɛ́ màↄ ku Lua pↄ́ ũ yã́i. Ma ga líwa ń Kilisio.
\v 20 Mapi má kú lↄo, Kilisi mɛ́ kú ma guu. Tiasa ma gbɛ̃nazĩnkɛ guu má kú Lua Nɛ́ pↄ́ yemazi à gì a wɛ̃nii ma yã́i náaikɛa guuɛ.
\v 21 Málɛ Lua gbɛ̃kɛ bãdɛo. Tó wì bↄ maa ikoyãpi yã́iɛ, Kilisi gà pãɛ.
\c 3
\s1 Mↄizi ikoyã ń luanaaikɛao
\p 
\v 1 Galati mìsaideↄ! Wa Yesu Kilisi gaa líwa sã́asã òɛ́ wásawasa. Wà pↄdàwá yã̀?
\v 2 Má ye mà yã́ mɛ̀ndo gbɛawá. A Lua Nisĩna è zĩkɛa ikoyãwa yã́i yã̀, ge yã́ pↄ́ á màpi náaikɛa yã́iɛ?
\v 3 Àkɛa a gↄ̃ mìsai kɛ́wai? Á dàalɛ ń Lua Nisĩna gbãaoɛ, ↄ̃ álɛ a midɛ ń ázĩa gbãao saa?
\v 4 A taasi saɛ kɛ̀ pã yã̀? Aↄ pão.
\v 5 Lua a Nisĩna kpàwá à dabudabuↄ kɛ̀ á guu á zĩkɛa ikoyãwa yã́i yã̀, ge yã́ pↄ́ á màpi náaikɛa yã́iɛ?
\p 
\v 6 À gwa Ablahaũwa. À Lua náaikɛ̀, ↄ̃ Lua tò yã́ bↄ̀aànↄ na.\f + \fr 3.6 \ft Daa 15.6, Lom 4.3\f*
\v 7 Àↄ dↄ̃ kɛ́ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa Lua náai vĩↄ mɛ́ Ablahaũ buiↄ ũ.\f + \fr 3.7 \ft Lom 4.16\f*
\v 8 Lua baonakpà Ablahaũɛ à mɛ̀ á báaada bui píigu aà sabai,\f + \fr 3.8 \ft Daa 12.3\f* asa wà dↄ̀aa wa kɛ̃̀ Luayãtaalau wà mɛ̀ Lua a to yã́ bↄ ń buipãleↄ na a náai pↄ́ aa kɛ yã́i.
\v 9 Beewa Lua ì báaada gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa a náaikɛ̀ↄgu, lá a kɛ̀ a náaikɛna Ablahaũɛwa.
\v 10 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ zɛ̀ ń zĩkɛa ikoyãwao gↄ̃̀ láaipↄ ũɛ, asa a kɛ̃a láu wà mɛ̀, gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ líↄ yã́ pↄ́ kú ikoyã lá guuↄ kũa píi a zɛ́waoá láaipↄɛ.\f + \fr 3.10 \ft Iko 27.26\f*
\v 11 Wá dↄ̃ sã́asã kɛ́ Lua lí tó yã́ bↄ̀ńnↄ na zĩkɛa ikoyãwa guuo, asa wà mɛ̀ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ Lua tò yã́ bↄ̀aànↄ na a náai pↄ́ àlɛ kɛ yã́i mɛ́ aↄ ku.\f + \fr 3.11 \ft Abk 2.4\f*
\v 12 Ikoyã i kↄ̃'e ń luanaaikɛaoo, asa wà mɛ̀ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ikoyãpi kũa mɛ́ a wɛ̃ni e a guu.\f + \fr 3.12 \ft Lev 18.5\f*
\v 13 Kilisi gↄ̃̀ láaipↄ ũ wá gbɛu, à wá bↄ́ ikoyã láai guu, asa a kɛ̃a láu wà mɛ̀, gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ wa lòo líwaá láaipↄɛ.\f + \fr 3.13 \ft Iko 21.23\f*
\v 14 Bee kɛ̀ màa kɛ́ báaa pↄ́ Lua dà Ablahaũgu e gↄ̃ buipãleↄnɛ Kilisi Yesu sabaiɛ, wí Nisĩna pↄ́ Lua a lɛgbɛ̃̀ e aà náaikɛa yã́i.
\s1 Mↄizi ikoyã ń Lua lɛgbɛ̃ao
\p 
\v 15 Ma gbɛ̃́ↄ, gbɛ̃nazĩn yãkɛa taa málɛ owàɛ́. Tó gbɛ̃́ lɛgbɛ dìlɛ mɛ́ a seeladeↄ vĩ, wa fↄ̃ wà a bãdɛo, wa fↄ̃ yãe kã́fĩuo.
\v 16 Beewa Lua lɛgbɛ̃̀ Ablahaũɛ ń aà buio. A kɛ̃a Luayãtaalau, wi mɛ ń aà buiↄ lán dasi wàlɛ owao,\f + \fr 3.16 \ft Daa 12.7\f* wà mɛ̀ ń aà buioɛ, gbɛ̃́ mɛ̀ndoɛ, ↄ̃n Kilisi ũ.
\v 17 Yã́ pↄ́ má ye on kɛ: Lua dↄ̀aa lɛgbɛ̃̀ɛ̀ yãa, à mɛ̀ a bàa àↄ kuaànↄ. A wɛ̃̀ ↄ̀aa pla ń baakwio (430) gbɛa ↄ̃ ikoyã mↄ̀.\f + \fr 3.17 \ft Bↄa 12.40\f* Ikoyãpi a fↄ̃ lɛgbɛ̃api gbooo, a fↄ̃ à a bãdɛo.
\v 18 Tó wì Lua báaa e zĩkɛa ikoyãwa guuɛ, báaapi a bↄ aà lɛgbɛ̃a guu lↄo. Lua gbɛ̃kɛkɛ̀ Ablahaũɛ kɛ́ à a lɛgbɛ̃̀ɛ̀ yã́iɛ.\f + \fr 3.18 \ft Lom 4.14\f*
\v 19 Bↄ́yãi à ikoyã dìlɛ lↄi? A kã̀fĩ e Ablahaũ bui pↄ́ Lua lɛgbɛ̃̀ aà yã́ musu àↄ mↄɛ, kɛ́ gbɛ̃́ↄ e dↄ̃ wa dɛ Luaɛ tàaedeↄ ũ yã́i. Lua a ikoyãpi kpà malaikaↄwa, aa nà kↄ́ↄɛ a ↄzĩ, ↄ̃ a dìlɛ gbɛ̃́ↄnɛ.
\v 20 Lua lɛgbɛ̃a sↄ̃, Luapi yã́ɛ ado, aà bàa kú ń kↄ́ↄeoo.
\p 
\v 21 Tↄ̀ↄ! Ikoyãpi bↄ̀ Lua lɛgbɛ̃a kpɛ yã̀? Màa no! Tó ikoyã pↄ́ ì wɛ̃ni kpámá kú yãa, dↄ̃ wa bↄ maa ikoyãpi sabai.
\v 22 A kɛ̃a Luayãtaalau wà mɛ̀, duuna gbɛ̃́pii kákpɛukɛ̀, kɛ́ báaa pↄ́ Lua a lɛgbɛ̃̀pi e gↄ̃ Yesu Kilisi náaikɛnaↄ pↄ́ ũ aà náai pↄ́ aalɛ kɛpi yã́i.
\p 
\v 23 Za dↄ̃ Yesu náaikɛa i mↄo, ikoyã wá kákpɛu kɛ̀, a wá kũa dakpɛunaↄ ũ e Yesu náaikɛa pↄ́ lɛ́ mↄ́ gɛ̀ bↄ̀ò.
\v 24 Beewa ikoyãpi dɛ wá gwana ũ yãa e Kilisi àↄ mↄ́, kɛ́ wà bↄ maa aà náaikɛa yã́i.
\v 25 Lá Yesu náaikɛa kà sa, wa bↄ wá gwana yã́u.
\p 
\v 26 Á naa Kilisi Yesuwa guu á dɛ Lua nɛ́ↄ ũ ápii aà náai pↄ́ álɛ kɛ yã́i,
\v 27 asa á gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ a da'ilɛkɛ̀ Kilisi pↄ́ ũↄ, a Kilisi dàɛ.
\v 28 Yudaↄ ń buipãleↄ, zↄↄ ń wɛ̃́ɛↄ, gↄ̃ɛↄ ń nↄɛↄ dodoa kↄ̃ɛo, asa ápiiá doũɛ naa Kilisi Yesuwa.
\v 29 Tó á dɛ Kilisi pↄ́ ũ, á dɛ Ablahaũ buiↄ ũɛ, mɛ́ á dɛ àizɛɛ pↄ́ Lua a lɛgbɛ̃̀ɛ̀ blenaↄ ũ.\f + \fr 3.29 \ft Lom 4.13\f*
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Málɛ oɛ́, gↄↄ pↄ́ túbiblena dɛ nɛ́ ũ, baa tó aà mae pↄ́ↄ dɛ aà pↄ́ ũ píi, a zↄ kɛ̃ao.
\v 2 Ì misiilɛ a gwanaↄnɛ ń ziiaↄ e gↄↄ pↄ́ aà mae dìlɛwa.
\v 3 Màa sↄ̃ wápiↄ, gↄↄ pↄ́ wi kàsaakũo, wi zↄble fɛlɛkaa pↄ́ pↄ́ wì misiilɛnɛ́ↄnɛ.\f + \fr 4.3 \ft Gal 4.9, Kls 2.8, 20\f*
\v 4 Kɛ́ gↄↄ pↄ́ Lua dìlɛ kà, à a Nɛ́ zĩ̀, wà aà ì gbɛ̃nazĩna iawa Mↄizi ikoyã guu,
\v 5 kɛ́ aà wá gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ Mↄizi yã́ iko vĩwáↄ bo, wí gↄ̃ a nɛ́ↄ ũ.
\v 6 Lua a Nɛ́ Nisĩna dà wá sↄ̃ guu, kɛ́ wá dɛ a nɛ́ↄ ũ yã́i. Nisĩnapi ì wiilɛ ì mɛ: Baa, ma Mae!
\v 7 Ayãmɛto zↄn n ũ lↄo, nɛ́n n ũ. Lá Lua Nɛ́n n ũ, à n kɛ a àizɛɛblena ũɛ.\f + \fr 4.7 \ft Lom 8.15-17\f*
\s1 Pↄlu bílikɛa Galatiↄwa
\p 
\v 8 Gↄↄ pↄ́ á Lua dↄ̃o, i zↄble pↄ́ pↄ́ aa dɛ Lua ũoↄnɛ.\f + \fr 4.8 \ft 1Kln 8.4-6\f*
\v 9 Lá a Lua dↄ̃̀ tiasa, atɛ̃sa kɛ́ Lua á dↄ̃́, bↄ́yãi a ɛa lɛ́ zɛ ń pↄ́ gia yãfũna gbãasaipiↄ lↄi? Bↄ́yãi a ɛa á ye zↄblenɛ́ dafu lↄi?
\v 10 I gↄↄeↄ ń mↄeↄ ń dikpɛeↄ ń wɛ̃eↄ tɛ̃bo.\f + \fr 4.10 \ft Lom 14.5, Kls 2.16\f*
\v 11 Vĩa ma kũ á yã́ musu. Asi taasi pã má kɛ̀ á guua?
\p 
\v 12 Ma gbɛ̃́ↄ, ma wabikɛ̀wá, à gↄ̃mawa, asa ma gↄ̃áwaɛ. Yãa i tàaekɛmɛɛo.
\v 13 Á dↄ̃ kɛ́ gyãekɛ guu ↄ̃ ma baonakpàuɛ́ sɛ̃́ia.
\v 14 Baa kɛ́ ma gyãkɛa kɛ̀ɛ́ yↄ̃a ũ, i sakamaguo, i gyaũkɛao, a ma si lán Lua malaika ge Kilisi Yesupiwaɛ.
\v 15 Báaa pↄ́ álɛ kɛmɛɛ yãa kɛ̀a ni? Má fↄ̃ o á yã́ musu, tó à zɛkɛ̀ yãa, á á wɛ́ bↄbↄ kpaaɛ.
\v 16 Kɛ́ ma sĩana'òɛ́ yã́i ↄ̃ ma gↄ̃ á zangude ũ saa?
\v 17 Gbɛ̃́piↄ kɛaɛ́ kɛ̀kɛ, i kɛ á maa yã́i no. Aa ye à kɛ̃́wáɛ, í namá.
\v 18 Wãa ń yãmaao gↄↄpii mɛ́ na, i kɛ gↄↄ pↄ́ má kúánↄ ado no.
\v 19 Ma nɛ́ yenzideↄ, málɛ á ia wãwãkɛ lↄ e Kilisi àↄ sadaágu.
\v 20 Má ye màↄ kúánↄ tia, mí a yã'oa lilɛ, asa ma bílikɛ̀ á yã́waɛ.
\s1 Hagaa ń Salao
\p 
\v 21 À omɛɛ, á gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ á ye misiilɛ ikoyãɛↄ, i ma lá a ku Mↄizi ikoyã guuo lé?
\v 22 Wà mɛ̀ Ablahaũ nɛgↄ̃ɛↄ ì gbɛ̃ↄn pla. À ado ì ń zↄoɛ,\f + \fr 4.22 \ft Daa 16.15\f* mɛ́ à ado ì ń wɛ̃́ɛo.\f + \fr 4.22 \ft Daa 21.1-2\f*
\v 23 Zↄpi nɛ'ì gbɛ̃nazĩnkɛ guuɛ, ↄ̃ wɛ̃́ɛ a pↄ́ ì Lua lɛgbɛ̃a yã́i.\f + \fr 4.23 \ft Lom 9.7-8\f*
\v 24 Nↄɛpiↄ yã́ dɛwɛ̃ɛ yãtaa ũ, Luabaakuańnↄ yã́ lɛɛ pla ũ. Ado bↄ̀ Sinai gbɛ kĩ́iɛ, ì zↄkɛ inɛ́. Bee mɛ́ Hagaa ũ.
\v 25 A dɛ Sinai gbɛ pↄ́ kú Laalubuↄ bùsuu yãtaa ũ. Yelusalɛũ tia dɛ a ũ lↄ, asa àlɛ zↄble ń a gbɛ̃́ↄ píiɛ.
\v 26 Yelusalɛũ pↄ́ kú musu mɛ́ wɛ̃́ɛ ũ. Ɔ̃mɛ wá da ũ.
\v 27 Asa a kɛ̃a láu wà mɛ̀:
\q1 Pↄnakɛ, fĩi pↄ́ ni nɛ'io!
\q1 Gulakɛ, n gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ni nↄwãwãkɛo!
\q1 Asa n gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ n gↄ̃ pãkpànzi,
\q1 n nɛ́ dasi aↄ dɛ nↄɛ pↄ́ a gↄ̃ aɛdↄ̀wà pↄ́a.\f + \fr 4.27 \ft Isa 54.1\f*
\m 
\v 28 Ápiↄ sↄ̃ ma gbɛ̃́ↄ, Lua lɛgbɛ̃a nɛ́ↄn á ũ lán Izaakiwa.
\v 29 Nɛ́ pↄ́ wa ì gbɛ̃nazĩnkɛ guu ĩadà nɛ́ pↄ́ wa ì ń Lua Nisĩna gbãaowa. Màa a dɛ ń a tiao.
\v 30 A kɛ̃a Luayãtaalau kpelewa ni? Wà mɛ̀: Zↄ yá ń a nɛ́o, asa zↄ nɛ́ a e túbible ń wɛ̃́ɛ nɛ́oo.\f + \fr 4.30 \ft Daa 21.9-10\f*
\v 31 Ayãmɛto ma gbɛ̃́ↄ, zↄ nɛ́ↄn wá ũo, wɛ̃́ɛ nɛ́ↄn wá ũ.
\c 5
\s1 Gↄ̃a wɛ̃́ɛↄ ũ
\p 
\v 1 Gↄ̃a wɛ̃́ɛↄ ũ yã́i Kilisi wá bói, wa gↄ̃ wɛ̃́ɛↄ ũ. À zɛò gíũgiũ, ásu to wà ɛa bakaɛ́ á níu zↄↄ ũ lↄo.
\p 
\v 2 Mámɛmaa Pↄlu málɛ oɛ́, tó á tò wà tↄ̃zↄ̃̀ɛ́, Kilisi a kã́fĩakɛɛ́o.
\v 3 Ma ɛa má ò ma idàwàɛ́, gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ tò wà tↄ̃zↄ̃̀ɛ, sema aà misiilɛ Mↄizi ikoyãɛ píi.
\v 4 Á gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ álɛ wɛɛlɛ à bↄ maa ikoyã guuↄ, a ázĩa kɛ̃̀ Kilisiwa, a kɛ̃ Lua gbɛ̃kɛwaɛ.
\v 5 Yesu náaikɛa guu wá dↄ̃ kɛ́ wá bↄ maa, wá wɛ́ dↄi ń aà Nisĩna gbãao.
\v 6 Naa Kilisi Yesuwa tↄ̃zↄ̃a ge tↄ̃zↄ̃sai yãe vĩo, sema Yesu náaikɛa pↄ́ ì to wàↄ yekↄ̃i.
\p 
\v 7 Álɛ gɛ́ aɛ yãa maamaaɛ. Démɛ tɛa sĩanai zɛzↄ̃̀ɛ́i?
\v 8 Yã́ pↄ́ álɛ e a zɛvĩpi i bↄ Lua pↄ́ á sisi à á sɛ́ kĩ́io.
\v 9 Pɛ̃ɛsɛ'ɛsɛ yↄↄna ì pɛ̃ɛti sɛ́ píi.\f + \fr 5.9 \ft 1Kln 5.6\f*
\v 10 Má á náai vĩ naa Diiwa guu kɛ́ á làasoo pãle kɛo. Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ lɛ́ á liaa sↄ̃, Lua a aà vãipi fĩaboɛ̀, baa dén nò.
\v 11 Mapi sↄ̃ ma gbɛ̃́ↄ, tó tↄ̃zↄ̃yã waaso málɛ kɛ e gbã, bↄ́yãi wàlɛ ma wɛtãi lↄi? Tó màaɛ, dↄ̃ Kilisi gaa líwa yã́ a ↄ̃ gbɛ̃ewao.
\v 12 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aalɛ á liaa ń tↄ̃zↄ̃yão, aa gɛ ńzĩa lɛ wi se.
\p 
\v 13 Ápiↄ sↄ̃ gbɛ̃́ↄ, Lua á sisi à gↄ̃ wɛ̃́ɛↄ ũɛ, ãma ásu tó á gↄ̃a wɛ̃́ɛↄ ũpi gↄ̃ɛ́ pↄeãkɛa zɛ́ ũo. Àↄ misiilɛkↄ̃ɛ àↄ yekↄ̃i,
\v 14 asa yã́ mɛ̀ndoɛ bee mɛ́ dɛ Mↄizi ikoyã píi mi ũ: Ǹyↄ̃ ye n gbɛ̃́deezi lá nzĩa wɛ̃niwa.
\v 15 Tó álɛ kↄ̃ soso kↄ̃ níwa, à laaika kↄ̃ kaalɛai.
\s1 Lua Nisĩna dↄaaanɛ́
\p 
\v 16 Málɛ oɛ́ à to Lua Nisĩna dↄaaɛ́, ázĩa pↄeã i midɛ.
\v 17 Ázĩa pↄeã lí kↄ̃'e ń Lua Nisĩna pↄ́oo, mɛ́ Lua Nisĩna pↄeã lí kↄ̃'e ń á pↄ́oo. Aa gìkↄ̃iɛ, ↄ̃ ili fↄ̃ yã́ pↄ́ á yei kɛ̀o.\f + \fr 5.17 \ft Lom 7.15-23\f*
\v 18 Tó Lua Nisĩna dↄaaaɛ́, Mↄizi yã́ iko vĩwáo.
\p 
\v 19 Wá wá dàa dↄ̃ wásawasa: Káaluakaa, gbãsĩkɛa, wisaiyã,
\v 20 tã́agbagbaa, gbɛ̃kↄↄlɛkɛa, ĩ́isɛa ń kↄ̃o, sòle, zangu, pↄkũma, dɛnlawɛɛlɛa, lɛkpaa, kↄ̃kpaalɛa,
\v 21 wɛdↄakↄ̃ɛ, wɛ̃dɛkɛa, lalasi kↄ̃̀ↄ ń yã́ bee taaↄ. Málɛ a lɛdawá lá má dàwá yãawa, yãbeetaakɛnaↄ kpala pↄ́ bↄ̀ Lua kĩ́i bleo.
\p 
\v 22 Lua Nisĩna sↄ̃ ì yã́ɛ beeↄ inɛ́: Yeakↄ̃i ń pↄnao ń aafiao ń mɛnao ń gbɛ̃kɛo ń maao ń náaio
\v 23 ń zĩabusaao ń zĩakũadↄ̃o. Ikoyãe lí gí yã́ beeↄ tàaeio.
\v 24 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ dɛ Kilisi Yesu pↄ́ ũↄ ń dàa pàliwa ń a pↄnidɛaↄ ń a pↄeãↄ sãnu.
\v 25 Lá wá kú Lua Nisĩna sabai, wà aà dↄ̀ↄ sɛ́.
\v 26 Wásu wàↄ yↄ̃̀ↄ vĩo, wásuli kↄ̃ pɛãao, wásuli wɛdↄkↄ̃ɛo.
\c 6
\s1 Ɔdaakↄ̃wa
\p 
\v 1 Gbɛ̃́ↄ, tó wasu gbɛ̃e kũ̀ ń zãa yã́wao, á gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ Lua Nisĩna dↄaaaɛ́ↄ, à gↄ̃́gↄ̃aànↄ busɛbusɛ, í laaika kɛ́ wasu á yↄ̃ sↄ̃o.
\v 2 À kↄ̃ aso sɛ́. Álɛ Kilisi ikoyã papan we.
\v 3 Tó gbɛ̃e lɛ́ azĩa gwa pↄ́ ũ mɛ́ a pↄe ũo, àlɛ azĩa sãsãɛ.
\v 4 Baade a yãkɛa tàasika, i gbasa ĩ́anadã. Asu a yãlɛɛũ ń gbɛ̃pãleoo,
\v 5 asa baade a azĩa aso sɛɛ.
\v 6 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ wàlɛ Lua yãdaɛ̀, aà a àizɛɛ lí a yãdanɛdeɛ.
\p 
\v 7 Ásu ázĩa sã́são, wìli kↄ̃nikɛ Luaɛo. Pↄ́ pↄ́ gbɛ̃́ tↄ̃̀ ↄ̃ ì kɛ̃́.
\v 8 Tó gbɛ̃́ tↄ̃̀ a dàa dↄaaaɛ guu, a kaalɛa iɛ̀. Tó gbɛ̃́ tↄ̃̀ Lua Nisĩna dↄaaaɛ guu sↄ̃, a wɛ̃ni láasai iɛ̀.
\v 9 Wásu kpasa ń maakɛaoo, asa tó wi kã́maboòo, wá ài'e a gↄↄwa.
\v 10 Ayãmɛto tó wa zɛ'è, wàli maakɛ gbɛ̃́piiɛ, atɛ̃sa wá Yesu náaikɛn deeↄ.
\s1 Lɛzaamá
\p 
\v 11 À wɛ̃̀sã gbɛ̃̀nɛgbɛ̃nɛ pↄ́ má kɛ̃̀ ń mazĩa ↄo gwa sa.
\v 12 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aalɛ yãkɛ wɛ́ yã́iↄ mɛ́ lɛ́ gãnawá ń tↄ̃zↄ̃yão, kɛ́ wasu ĩadamá zɛa ń Kilisi gaa líwao yã́ musuo yã́iɛ.
\v 13 Baa tↄ̃̀zↄ̃napiↄ se, aa ikoyã kũao. Aa ye à tↄ̃zↄ̃ kɛ́ wà e ĩ́anadã á seelapi musu yã́iɛ.
\v 14 Má ĩ́anadã pↄe yã́ musuo, sema wá Dii Yesu Kilisi gaa líwa yã́ bàasio, asa a yã́i dṹnia gↄ̃̀mɛɛ gɛ ũ mɛ́ ma gↄ̃ gɛ ũ dṹniaɛ.
\v 15 Tↄ̃zↄ̃a ge tↄ̃zↄ̃sai yãe vĩo, sema gↄ̃a gbɛ̃́ dafu ũ.
\v 16 Lua gbɛ̃kɛkɛ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ yã́pi kũaↄnɛ, i ń gba aafia. Aamɛ aa Isaili sĩanaↄ ũ.
\p 
\v 17 Za gbã gbɛ̃e su ma wɛtã lↄo. Ĩa pↄ́ wa dàa Yesu yã́i gbɛ ku ma mɛwa.
\p 
\v 18 Gbɛ̃́ↄ, wá Dii Yesu Kilisi gbɛ̃kɛkɛ á nisĩnaɛ! Ãmi.
